        {
            "title": "滙控據報洽售德國基金管理業務 最快數周內達成協議",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"滙控據報洽售德國基金管理業務 最快數周內達成協議\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/20f11559d8aeda8dc924283c67ae0d53/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250320/_2025032010130872897.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">滙控據報洽售德國基金管理業務 最快數周內達成協議</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>據彭博引述消息報道，滙控（005）正與私募股權公司BlackFin Capital Partners就出售德國基金管理業務（Inka）進行深入談判，雙方最快在未來數周內達成協議。滙控則在一份聲明表示，正評估德國證券服務業務的戰略選項，目前尚未做出任何決定。\n\n</p><h2>法巴或購德國托管業務</h2>\n<p>同時，法國巴黎銀行正就收購滙豐德國托管業務進行談判，目前尚未達成最終協議，也可能出現其他買家。\n\n</p>\n<p>報道又提到，Inka資產管理規模約4,000億歐元。彭博早前亦指，滙控正將Inka與德國託管業務一起向潛在買家推介，兩者售價可能達到數億歐元。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2059185/即時-財經-滙控據報洽售德國基金管理業務-最快數周內達成協議",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-20 10:17:06",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "九龍灣企廣全層意向價9660萬 每呎6000元",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"九龍灣企廣全層意向價9660萬 每呎6000元\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/86123f2ab63e1f104cec96715b176517/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250320/_2025032010115148593.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">九龍灣企廣全層意向價9660萬 每呎6000元</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>美聯商業高級營業董事黃璜表示，九龍灣宏照道39號企業廣場3期高層全層單位放售，建築面積約16,100方呎，意向價約9,660萬，平均每方呎價約6,000元。資料顯示，大廈對上一宗成交為低層單位，建築面積約2,200呎，於2021年以約2,000萬易手，每呎約9,091元，放售的全層單位較高峰期低逾30%。\n\n</p><h2>意向價約9660萬</h2>\n<p>黃璜表示，該廈由嘉里發展，為區內地標甲廈，此次放售高層全層極罕有，樓底高達3.75米，配備寫字樓裝修，享維港景，單設專用通道前往洗手間，企業廣場3期配備14部載客電梯及1部載貨電梯，並設升高地台，承重達5kpa，大廈設有Fusion Cafe，為用戶提供餐飲選擇。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4147816/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"九龍灣企業廣場3期高層放售，意向價約9660萬。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/41bfc5d42cdfa3c72bb9938a156a8c49/2025-03/PRO07P02130723.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        九龍灣企業廣場3期高層放售，意向價約9660萬。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2059184/即時-地產-九龍灣企廣全層意向價9660萬-每呎6000元",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-20 10:17:06",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "深水埗盲人按摩店女顧客拔罐搶火 背脊及手二級燒傷送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警員在按摩店調查。林思明攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/baf933e0d314a2471e645d43762754b8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250320/_2025032010061339000.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警員在按摩店調查。林思明攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>深水埗發生拔罐意外。今日（20日）早上8時56分，一名女子在長沙灣道47號地下一間盲人按摩店，進行按摩及拔火罐治療，其間懷疑職員噴灑精油突然搶火，火舌燒着女事主的背部，並波及睡床。職員見狀連忙將火撲熄，女事主背部及右手灼傷，報警求助。救護員到場將她送往明愛醫院治理，其間有女警陪同。現場消息稱，女事主經送院後證實二級燒傷，警方正調查事件原因。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4147795/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"女傷者由救護車送院。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f0c54e84697f9a4ace3ac99eb11e14c0/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250320_095405271.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女傷者由救護車送院。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4147796/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"女警陪同女傷者送院。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/196740ff3157487386d18314411758c0/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250320_095405271_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女警陪同女傷者送院。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4147789/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"涉事的盲人按摩中心位於長沙灣道47號地下。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cbaecbde40d6b71adef38601a3d6fd20/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250320_095114231.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉事的盲人按摩中心位於長沙灣道47號地下。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4147790/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"按摩店負責人（灰衣者）協助警員調查。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/86731fa15e93d5acd1aff6211d3ead5f/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250320_095114231_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        按摩店負責人（灰衣者）協助警員調查。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4147791/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f2eb5d34ee23e8b5ac57386658752