            "title": "英超｜車路士落實打包士砵亭雙星 一原因成功搶走曼聯艾摩廉心頭好",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"車路士主帥馬列斯卡(左)與曼聯主帥魯賓艾摩廉(右)。Getty\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/0f4b52c4fdea9ed93039758b9113f3b9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250320/_2025032009452326159.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">車路士主帥馬列斯卡(左)與曼聯主帥魯賓艾摩廉(右)。Getty</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>士砵亭周三發官方聲明宣布，兩位新星翼衛昆達和中場伊蘇高將轉投車路士，轉會費合共最高可達7,740萬歐羅。曼聯主帥魯賓艾摩廉乃昆達的恩師，故盛傳前者很想帶愛徒到曼聯，然而車路士卻殺出成巧搶走，據報其中關鍵是主帥馬列斯卡親自遊說。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"昆達。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5d79f49dee350272acc292fe610e583e/2025-03/GettyImages-2195483127.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        昆達。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"昆達。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3783c6f4446d32b469807c241cd43bd6/2025-03/GettyImages-2195489928.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        昆達。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"伊蘇高。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f2fa7826e730bdf26afaa67884a7ca80/2025-03/GettyImages-2180073078.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        伊蘇高。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"伊蘇高。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c7fcd4c4be9a033d9804cb7d81da71df/2025-03/GettyImages-2204192661.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        伊蘇高。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯主帥艾摩廉。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fe1e95dfc4e4386010a21c4b95b95385/2025-03/GettyImages-2202857201.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯主帥艾摩廉。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯主帥艾摩廉。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2340d4c8acbed477f3c3769ce777f43b/2025-03/GettyImages-2204961703.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯主帥艾摩廉。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車路士主帥馬列斯卡。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5e4ad2805619d68f009936f0d1cf49bc/2025-03/GettyImages-2205387171.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車路士主帥馬列斯卡。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車路士主帥馬列斯卡。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3fca91626e5a1189ef186d97aaec1473/2025-03/GettyImages-2190116912.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車路士主帥馬列斯卡。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>士砵亭官宣雙星轉投車路士</h2>\n<p>士砵亭周三率先單方面官方宣布與車路士達成協議，將昆達和伊蘇高打包賣給藍獅。其中昆達的固定轉會費約5,100萬歐羅，另加135萬歐羅浮動條款。而此子下季將續效力士砵亭，至2026至2027球季才正式加盟車路士。至於目前被外借至拉斯彭馬斯的伊蘇高的轉會費約2,220萬歐羅，他則會於下季立即加入車路士。\n\n</p><h2>主帥出馬搶走曼聯心頭好</h2>\n<p>17歲右翼衛昆達於今季獲時任士砵亭主帥艾摩廉賞識提拔至一隊，立即坐穩正選，成為歐洲矚目新星之一。此前一早盛傳艾摩廉十分渴望師徒在曼聯重聚，於今夏收購昆達，但礙於財政問題令曼聯未能提前出手，最終意外地被車路士截胡。而其中關鍵因素之一是藍獅主帥馬列斯卡親自遊說，給予了昆達極大信心，告訴後者要不斷進步、學習和提高，並認定此子是車路士未來大計的完美人選，明言期待未來一起工作。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
